athrm{y}}{\\mathrm{dt}^{2}}=\\mathrm{a}=-2 \\omega^{2} \\sin \\left(\\omega \\mathrm{t}+\\frac{\\pi}{3}\\right)\r\n\r\n$$\r\n\r\n$a_{\\max }=-2 \\omega^{2}=g$\r\n\r\nFor which mass just breaks off the plank $\\omega=\\sqrt{\\mathrm{g} / 2}$\r\n\r\nThis will be happen for the first time when\r\n\r\n$$\r\n\r\n\\begin{array}{l}\r\n\r\n\\omega \\mathrm{t}+\\frac{\\pi}{3}+\\frac{\\pi}{2} \\text { or } \\omega \\mathrm{t}=\\frac{\\pi}{6} \\\\\r\n\r\n\\therefore \\quad \\mathrm{t}=\\frac{\\pi}{6 \\omega}=\\frac{\\pi}{6} \\sqrt{\\frac{2}{\\mathrm{~g}}}\r\n\r\n\\end{array}\r\n\r\n$$", "image": null}, "videoSolution": null, "numericalUpperLimit": null, "numericalLowerLimit": null, "questionLabels": [], "__v": 0, "masterId": "MOGBSPYQ91073381", "bucket": "", "category": null, "microConcepts": [], "imageBaseUrl": null, "helperText": null, "isRemoved": false, "cpyqbSubjects": ["61bb58181213731910ea0b70", "61c055eae8ce0dc8a5c62d33", "616057750283de43c87e3e1b", "61964fe0a5a5260118868021", "61964f81a5a526011886801d", "629f39e4ac11b26562e0625b", "616057920283de43c87e3e1e", "615f0c729476412f48314dab", "61a8a2c2e8ce0dc8a5c62d2d", "629105adee9e3ae00d63352b", "629f385f263330a77be9fa7d", "616056cd0283de43c87e3e15", "616057190283de43c87e3e18", "62962075e7f8e9ac4daeafd7", "64d50bd73df7f4a7f3017f6f", "66b79b34d4b564dfab4f94cc", "678ea9a09cc79e5f592bdc11", "67fa5fef4468eb1307ceb0ad", "6807d2ad647479b8e8696479"], "cpyqbChapters": ["616023f6105ab3ae165341bb", "61964c8546e3d33b1892d09e", "61c089968734366dae3f36bc", "61bb8217aebeece6abdbe72b", "616023f783ceaeb51fe46126", "616023f4946fab7b921bf28d", "61964c86b98428bab9bd89d6", "616023f51f5c75c27ba35382", "616023f36324da677f8a7444", "61e7bd75347c64f272d9d8bb", "62962124ca45d71899e3dfe9", "629f390dd4f42c0deef34eab", "629109ef78779344f598426c", "629f3a921cf4dc490b09a322", "64eb06c13118f713ecfef085", "66d5853ca75f05ee8564f57b", "67921d681d5b5072da5e9acb", "67fdff4e378e1624ea7b69f4", "6809202b3a10446a207fdee4"], "cpyqbExams": ["61a8a124e8ce0dc8a5c62d2